# Configuration surface

When changing behavior, prefer these files (commit together when semantics shift):

| File | Role |
| --- | --- |
| `config/agents.json` | Agent registry graph |
| `config/orchestration_dag.json` | Wave schedule |
| `config/orchestration.json` | Linear flow narrative |
| `config/skills.json` | Skill → agent ownership |
| `config/guardrails.json` | Guardrail path mapping |
| `config/jira_agent_assignees.json` | Jira assignee routing |
| `config/workflow_config.json` | PR lifecycle orchestrator |

Python automation: `agents/jira_story_generator.py`, `agents/github_pr_description_writer.py`, `orchestrator/pr_lifecycle_orchestrator.py`.
